msgctxt "56_Isawa"
msgid "*gasp* *wheeze* You mother... *cough*"
msgstr "*jadea* *suspira* Hijo de... *tose*"

msgctxt "68_Fay"
msgid "Tanimura-san, are you okay? Are you hurt!?"
msgstr "Tanimura, ¿estás bien? ¿¡Te has hecho daño!?"

msgctxt "80_Isawa"
msgid "...You serious, Fay? You ain't just fuckin' with me? Are\\r\n"
"you really tryin' to do me dirty like this?"
msgstr "¿...en serio, Fay? ¿No te estás quedando conmigo?\\r\n"
"¿De verdad me vas a joder de esta manera?"

msgctxt "92_Fay"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "104_Isawa"
msgid "Fine. I'll just step back and let you think about it... But\\r\n"
"don't forget that you'll never make it without me. You're a\\r\n"
"nobody going nowhere in life. Oh, and enjoy your new prick."
msgstr "Bueno. Daré un paso al costado y te dejaré meditarlo...\\r\n"
"Pero no olvides que no eres nada sin mí. Una donnadie\\r\n"
"sin rumbo por la vida. Ah, y disfruta de tu nueva verga."

msgctxt "176_Tanimura"
msgid "Are... you okay?"
msgstr "¿Estás... bien?"

msgctxt "188_Fay"
msgid "I am... now that it's over between Isawa and me. I can't thank you enough, Tanimura-san."
msgstr "Sí... ahora que terminó lo mío con Isawa sí. No puedo \\r agradecerte lo suficiente, Tanimura."

msgctxt "200_Tanimura"
msgid "Well, at least he got <Italic>some</Italic> sense knocked into him...\\r\n"
"But it's fairly obvious that he's the type to hold a grudge.\\r\n"
"I should give you my number so you can call me just in case."
msgstr "Bueno, al menos <Italic>alguna</Italic> idea le acomodé ahí arriba... Pero\\r \n"
"es bastante obvio que es de los que guardan rencor.\\r \n"
"Debería darte mi número por si acaso."

msgctxt "224_Fay"
msgid "Yes, please do that. That's... very thoughtful, Tanimura-san."
msgstr "Sí, por favor. Es... muy buena idea, Tanimura."

msgctxt "260_Tanimura"
msgid "Well, I'm off. Hope your money makes it back home safely\\r\n"
"from now on."
msgstr "Bueno, me voy. Espero que ahora el dinero llegue a casa\\r\n"
"sin problemas."

msgctxt "272_Fay"
msgid "Yes... Oh, and before I forget... I'd like you to have this."
msgstr "Sí... Ah, antes de que me olvide... Quiero que te quedes \\r con esto."

msgctxt "308_Fay"
msgid "I guess this is goodbye... Maybe you can swing by my work sometime? Just a thought."
msgstr "Supongo que es un 'adiós'... Si quisieras te podrías pasar \\r por mi trabajo algún dia. Es solo una idea."

msgctxt "344_Tanimura"
msgid "Whew... Never thought it'd feel so good to be single.\\r\n"
"On that note, I should get back to work myself."
msgstr "Uf... Nunca pensé que se sentiría tan bien ser soltero.\\r\n"
"Hablando de eso, debería volver a trabajar en mi mismo."

